{"tid":1681890,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[正視聽] 接受鶳","createTime":"2019-10-29T16:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T13:09:08.000Z","uid":106368,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9c25cfaa1594c5c83b6ca2bb1addd924969ed1e5","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"112我估都會有呢啲場面 想大家精神心態上打個底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你縱容啲畜生 就係允許佢繼續有機會禍害手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n藍屍/休班狗攻擊我哋嘅手足同埋路人，有人出去支援幫拖，但就比人鬧係去送頭、中計、愚蠢。其實呢啲言論，同啲狗口中講嘅「你唔出現喺嗰度就冇事」 係一樣：你唔咁蠢去撩藍屍咪冇事、你唔去還拖咪唔會受傷、你唔去幫手狗咪唔會拉你&mdash;&mdash;呢班不諳文明嘅畜生周圍威脅、攻擊我哋嘅人，本來就係衝住我哋而嚟，我哋縮得一次，佢哋下次都仍然會追打、追斬我哋嘅手足。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解大家唔係群起而出，反而係指責啲出嚟對抗嘅人？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住無視佢哋，我哋嘅手足就唔會受傷&mdash;&mdash;正正係因為一開始我哋縱容佢哋，以為幾件藍屍畜生唔會做到啲乜，今日佢哋成班烏合之眾越嚟越惡，有恃無恐咁周圍撕紙、斬人。大家仲記唔記得荃灣比人斬手斬腳嘅兄弟？仲記唔記得喺連儂牆俾畜生斬到入ICU嘅姊妹？記唔記得的士狗撞斷手足對腳？我哋話要報仇、要血償，今日有人去報仇卻俾你哋講成中計。<br />\n<br />\n721元朗白衫畜生都係有組織咁攻擊我哋，當日我哋尚且識得組隊反抗、護住手足返屋企，點解今日退化到指責自己人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「維持道德高地」、「智取」、「中計」、「中共技倆」&mdash;&mdash;呢啲統統只係用嚟掩飾自己怯懦嘅藉口。真正嘅道德，唔係打不還手，而係阻止不義嘅出現；由我哋擔當起保衛香港嘅責任，去保護香港人不被畜生騷擾。當有落單嘅畜生就打斷佢哋手腳；有一堆畜生喺度發瘟，我哋就應該一齊反抗，保護身邊手足。 <br />\n<br />\n執行公義一向係理所當然的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n同埋我唔該一班阻膠 你地唔同意咪行遠啲唔好睇 咪撚喺度扮大愛保護畜生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e4f420861d59f4084cd5cf7d9e4c5097e320339","tid":1681890,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T16:59:38.000Z","msg":"$1交稅攬炒機械人小測成績表已出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679773\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679773</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a64cd7e776d84928f943cb287fce29adcca8ab5","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"自推10次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1hFX9T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1hFX9T.jpg&h=5b17d60b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"870c969eea736877baf30faf655ccdaf0a39c62d","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:31:59.000Z","msg":"2<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JPdyTD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JPdyTD.jpg&h=2df9ca68&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48827992048ca6a1f85c6839b9dabbb39a9bec64","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"3<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tQLgwFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtQLgwFA.jpg&h=62cd39a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c35d016896ec560de8d94a4270e7b4955b6f2515","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:33:20.000Z","msg":"4<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QDSVNd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQDSVNd4.jpg&h=c91b40a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cAPUikL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAPUikL.jpg&h=7d7d9a0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8473f43e8b2a96511be81b600bea839cb37e763b","tid":1681890,"uid":106368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T17:34:18.000Z","msg":"5<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M367Dk4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM367Dk4.jpg&h=abeb9acc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8635f8fe1cdff63962c